divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband took this picture of me at the Coit Tower in San Francisco CA. When we came back home from our vacation I put all our pictures on my computer. One day I was playing with them and I noticed an object on the top left corner of this picture. I have no idea where this came from. Can you help identifying this object? thanks!
